{"about_the_game":"Manafall is a VR Tower-Defense game that melds strategy and action. Set in a magical-fantasy world, the player will fight through hordes of enemies using swords and bows, while casting spells, and building towers.<br><br><br><strong><u>BUILD YOUR DEFENSES</u></strong><br>Build towers to aid in your defense. The towers can be upgraded and branch-out to other tower types. Each tower has a specific purpose, element and damage type.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291140/extras/Towers.png?t=1678314370\" /><br><br><strong><u>CAST SPELLS</u></strong><br>You can equip up to 4 spells per hand and 4 skills for offensive equipment.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291140/extras/Spells.png?t=1678314370\" /><br><br><strong><u>SUMMON YOUR VANGUARD</u></strong><br>Call-out your Vanguard to aid your front-line of your defense. A Vanguard team is composed of 3 to 5 units, hand-picked by the player.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291140/extras/Vanguard.png?t=1678314370\" /><br><br><strong><u>STRATEGIZE</u></strong><br>You can switch between a Strategic View and a First-Person View with a button press. In the Strategic View, you can build, upgrade, move and sell towers, as well as see the incoming waves. You can also build normally while in FPS View.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291140/extras/Strategic.png?t=1678314370\" /><br><br><br><strong><u>CHOOSE YOUR ARSENAL</u></strong><br>You can choose to equip Swords, Bows and Shields.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291140/extras/Arsenal.png?t=1678314370\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291140/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1678314370","